Junius Matthews https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Junius_Matthews 0 Junius Conyers Matthews (June 12, 1890 – January 18, 1978) was an American actor and voice actor. He was the original voice of Rabbit in the Winnie the Pooh franchise from 1966 to 1977. Junius_Conyers_Matthews ( June_12_,_1890 – January_18_,_1978 ) was an_American_actor_and_voice_actor .
